    "title": "Mid-Level Radiologist at Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "If you're a passionate Radiologist with drive and ambition, Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions in Vadodara is the place for you. We're growing fast and need talented people to grow with us.\n\nAbout Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions:\nIpca Laboratories Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Provide high-quality patient care and maintain patient records\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n• Participate in quality improvement initiatives and clinical audits\n• Maintain accurate clinical documentation in electronic health records\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Respond to medical emergencies and provide immediate care\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Wound Care\n• Proficiency in Surgical Procedures\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Medical Terminology\n• Proficiency in Clinical Research\n• Proficiency in NABH Standards\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vadodara, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ipca Laboratories Ventures Solutions!",
